Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  義賀先生托我們運送的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那邊的東西讓我們製造部來送？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道  說是之後會讓人到現場去取
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行啦  快點  要去送了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  木村先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生都說暫時先觀察一下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  難得的硫加…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加那傢伙真沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也許能成為合適的宿主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托  基加的現在位置是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,經過6號首都高速道路  正向著向島方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快  怎麼了  等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你稍微安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  以我的速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓你安靜一會了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去了  掉下去了  掉下去了  掉下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼沒穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的意識恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請別害怕  千川功君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…你怎麼知道我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快點醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我醒著的哦  只是在考慮該怎麼開口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川功君  今天一天已經對你的情況大致…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰呀  在哪  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在你體內哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  應該說你在我體內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點  現在就給你說明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣看好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面  功君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是巴迪·希馮  宇宙聯邦警察的搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隱居用的假身份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正追著某個重犯在地球展開潛入調查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  我就單刀直入的說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實昨天在追蹤犯人的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  功君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲…蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你處於死的狀態  千川功君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是宇宙聯邦警察特搜部的麥基烏斯警官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為巴迪的上司  對您表示歉意及哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身體已經送往艾克諾斯奎爾的醫學研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那嘗試再構成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會有段時間不大方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這段時間你的肉體由巴迪來替代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說你依然可以作為千川功照常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼我完全聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死了什麼的  哀悼什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是活得好好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無法相信我說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起你說的話  蟲子開口說話更讓人難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為你這樣驚慌失措才讓基加逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去了  掉下去了  掉下去了  掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  車開過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  我的閃閃發亮的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的寶貝在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的寶貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托  基加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾  跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊  是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然被扔到高速公路上  怎麼能保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把她給我趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管你是不是什麼外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的身體內留有別人的意識我絕對拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君  有一點你理解錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這是什麼  身體這樣不是死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  簡單來說就是讓你的意識躲到了巴迪體內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生命是靠巴迪的身體維持著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是巴迪在你體內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你在巴迪體內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身體修復之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:09:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生命和意識都只能寄存在巴迪體內
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噩夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身心俱疲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  連吃驚的力氣都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就容我自我介紹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫帝托  是巴迪的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的事情我也有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼我能做的就通過巴迪隨時跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噩夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼消沉嘛  我知道錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  功君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一成不變的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的一天的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,往常看慣的景物  今早卻如此刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…已經死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「對不起」我不都說了好多遍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「還是個男子漢呢」地球上是這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「還是個男子漢呢  這麼糾纏不休」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是不要煩個不停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說我倆不能像心靈感應那樣在腦海中對話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣做的話  有可能會導致精神融合的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,練習一下在口中說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種像腹語似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大清早的嘀嘀咕咕的說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮  嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  早上心情就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又做奇怪的夢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  硬要說的話  我個人覺得自己變成廢墟了  哼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼什麼的不適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早  北村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒聽說嗎  中杉同學的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天出車禍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:12:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是在中杉同學常去的醫院歸來的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但願不是重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看望一下不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們關係不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像參加葬禮似的無精打采  還是等看過之後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別說不吉利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了悼念死者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  通過火化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  火化就是火葬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是燒成灰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  呀  剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這是有很複雜的原因的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之今天大家一起去看望她  行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在意識還沒有恢復  仍處於危險期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們盡全力了  或許還是有必要做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我的鼻子可是宇宙第一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那確實是阿留多人的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說硫加…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  一定是巴迪那傢伙拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  虧我特地讓這個星球的人來運送的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥因為暴露了長相無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我來代替你去拿回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的相貌還沒暴露  管他什麼「狂戰士殺手」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相對的  我把她吃了行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓得受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  是依露瑪辦事處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直承蒙您照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  有田紫苑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  果然有空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,電視的拍攝  這可有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會化妝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我想那樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,17點  八幡攝影場對吧  那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同學一場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罷了罷了  多一個人  中杉同學也更開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  千川是不是太慢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  都那樣提醒他別遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  好慢呀  遲到了喲  遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  紫苑  嚴守時間可是這個業界的鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了呐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什麼「怎麼了呐」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醫院那邊怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是要和大家一起去看望中杉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君因為預定計劃突然改變而生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這可是藝人和演藝圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個世界活下去可是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們活下去是要做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位姑娘  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老毛病…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好心人將壞人打倒  將鎮上的姑娘救走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,登場的就是這些  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  應該是5點開拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是衝擊波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀  打偏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把硫加還來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說乾脆被我吃掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴齊魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別用那個名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著基加有什麼企圖  巴齊魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身體換多了連記憶都混亂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要交出硫加的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  他是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:17:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是聯邦正在通緝的重犯  巴齊魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寄生在別的生物上生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就可以吸取對方的記憶甚至知識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是外星人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  但那個身體是地球人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是被他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  那樣就能知道硫加在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼  巴迪  快撤出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  來了  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能讓你吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那個女的就是有田紫苑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個搜查官  吃掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  有人  有人倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更換了身體後我還會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又要殺人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又要增加像我這樣的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  只是暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是室戶先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識他？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室戶圭介  我們學校的畢業生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自稱是記者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  有人要來了  撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨  竟然就這樣厚著臉皮逃回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  再不快點行動的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加丟失的事情要是被夏瑪朗或者戈梅斯知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  這個身體已經是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子好餓  肚子好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼意思啊  昨天不去探病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,電話也不通  你就是這麼絕情的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這裡面有很多原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  中杉怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天謝謝你們來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好的嗎  沒什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,輪不到你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別那麼生氣嘛  今後要共處一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  用你們的話來說就是…什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人…  兩人三腳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吳越同舟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  就是那個  就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倆好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
